<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.995858>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 13. Carvalhoiella montandoni. (8) Dorsal habitus, (9) abdominal terga VI and VII of male, (10) abdominal tergum VIII of male with pseudoparameres, (11) male genital capsule, (12) male genital capsule with terga IX and X (proctiger) removed, (13) ventral surface of phallosoma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/995858/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

